---
title: Szechuan Chicken Stir-Fry with Mushrooms, Mangetout and Rice
description: Full of sweet and savoury notes with a bit of a kick, Szechuan (pronounced sich-waan) paste is the perfect pairing for both meat and veggie stir-fry dishes.
